{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Is everyone just fending for themselves - or is there any empathy left after all?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Facing the rain&quot; is a story-driven RPG, without battles but with impactful decisions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take the role of Billy, a young girl embarking on her first job\u00a0as a hotel maid, in a town called Drumberg - which is nowhere in particular. Soon she realizes, there is a tragic heaviness weighing down on the hotel and its people. But she has the power to transform the place - if she makes the right choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras/about_animation.gif?t=1734388048\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game interactively tells a fictional yet relatable story centered around themes of grief and depression, but also positivity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player\u2019s actions will determine the outcome of the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Guide your character through an immersive 2D pixel-graphics-based world. Make your way to the hotel, discover the building and its surroundings, go into town and visit shops, and explore a metaphorical forest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with other characters: The player will meet different types of characters that present opinions or problems that require to engage thoughtfully.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the main plot, you will collect items and solve problems or puzzles in an adventure-style manner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover secrets and succeed in challenges to unlock achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Randomized elements add variety to each playthrough, enhancing the game\u2019s replay value.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Contains original music crafted exclusively for the story that is being told.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Playtime is roughly 2-3 hours. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras/maennchen_transparent.png?t=1734388048\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Controls:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keyboard: WASD or Cursor buttons (configurable)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller supported (Xbox, Dualshock via USB)<br><i>We recommend launching the game with &quot;Disable Steam Input&quot; option under Properties -&gt; Controller</i></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Cleaner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/bb7f62741def27b57907723b35e1553058270961.jpg"},{"name":"Arrival","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/2c7b28a8d13c6b291ee2d7dca7e3fdebd2887559.jpg"},{"name":"Day1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/cab03768d15ebf34739895fe44b5d013d66f73a3.jpg"},{"name":"Forest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/f5e08862c13f67639725156371207a34fb15850e.jpg"},{"name":"Day2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/24f9add53ef206131c323d9c2b74b1b98dc49b67.jpg"},{"name":"Empathy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/ac4c30b817019af6be887c0b952f0522868ffc39.jpg"},{"name":"Day3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3294370/021ad1e05bbef30b5c1327aaa99ae969e5190fc0.jpg"},{"name":"Winner","path":"https://cdn.akama